name: Wooden Blocks Set of 6 Perfectly Pink and Brown
description:
Set of 6, 2 inch wood blocks. This set does not include letters but they can easily be added. The edges have been sanded. The blocks are covered with six different styles of paper and sealed several times with a non-toxic varnish. Can easily be cleaned with a damp cloth. These are a great educational toddler toy. A canvas storage bag is included with no additional charge.

Please keep in mind even though these blocks are covered with a non-toxic sealant and the edges are sanded it is recommended these be used with adult supervision. All blocks are hand cut and sanded by Magens Bay Designs and might slightly vary in size. The pattern shown in the pictures may vary depending on the placement of the paper.

description:
